name: Rare Jeeode
description: In the pursuit of pure impartiality, the Rare Jeeode has achieved near-perfection. Its commitment to resolving conflicts between fellow monsters is so strong, it even endows fragments of itself with all-seeing eyes. Perhaps this is taking the idea of 'seeing' both sides of story too literally. They can, at times, be a little creepy.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 1 day 21 hr, Enhanced Time: 1 day 10 hr 7 min 30 sec
